Pygruta release notes
=====================

1.49
----

* New features:

A new SQLite driver.

[Gemini] Snapshot also generates atom.xml.

1.48
----

* New features:

Stories can now be written in Gemini (Gemtext) format and rendered to HTML.

A new command line option has been added, `gemini-snapshot', to generate a snapshot of Gemini (.gmi) files. Only stories in Gemini format will be generated, as well as an index.gmi file liking all of them in reverse date order.

The special URI mail: (analog to mailto:) is supported.
